    "We also propose collaboration among organizations and industries to standardize maintenance terminology and jargon, which would enable the construction of large corpora for maintenance text.",
    "TLP can also be extended to other areas of manufacturing with the abundance of text data.",
    "Quality inspection logs generate a lot of text data on which TLP can be used to help determine whether a product needs to be reworked/scrapped.",
